# Google OAuth web client ID for Google Identity Services (GIS).
# Create at https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
#   - Application type: Web application
#   - Authorized JavaScript origins: http://127.0.0.1:5173 (dev) and your Vercel URL
#   - OAuth scope used by the app: https://www.googleapis.com/auth/drive.appdata
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in the value.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-web-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com
